  "section_name": "Financial Analysis",
  "text": "Airbnb demonstrated strong revenue recovery in Q2 2025, posting revenue of $3,096,000,000 (C002), representing 36.27% year-over-year growth compared to Q2 2024's $2,748,000,000 (K001). This marks a significant rebound from Q1 2025, which saw a -39.12% YoY decline to $2,272,000,000 (K001), reflecting the company's seasonal business patterns. The Q3 2024 period showed particularly strong performance at $3,732,000,000 with 35.81% YoY growth (K001), indicating robust travel demand during peak seasons. The sequential improvement from Q1 to Q2 2025 suggests normalization following the weaker early-year performance.",
